videos.description: Tom Izzo is proud of the character of his team, getting tough in overtime to avoid the upset against Oakland without Spartans star Denzel Valentine.
videos.headline: Izzo says defense needed work

videos.description: Jordan Bernfield and Brooke Weisbrod recap Michigan State's overtime victory over Oakland.
videos.headline: Michigan State finds a way to win
